          "text": "h(t) is absolutely integrable"
        },
        {
          "key": "B",
          "text": "h(t) is finite"
        },
        {
          "key": "C",
          "text": "h(t) = 0 for t<0"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "h(t) > 0"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "h(t) is absolutely integrable",
      "explanation": "BIBO stability requires absolute integrability of impulse response: ∫|h(t)|dt < ∞. This ensures bounded output for bounded input.",
